channel.title: [508/525]Project Warzone
channel.description:
Project Warzone started out as just a PulsePk base, Hosted only for friends. Then It got boring briding the same people, so I advertised a bit and reached up to a good 42+ active players. Im releasing this cause I've started a 317 which is getting better and better everyday. This server is great just to download and host, cause it has multiple pk spots. [B]You should modify the ::item command cause i made it so everyone can spawn on the last day. [/B]
Features: [CODE] No Off-screen autocast Perfect Hybriding/Tri No lag when switching armour (ex.- Full mystic to Full rune) All Godsword Special Attacks Dds specs are perfect Full Mage Miasmic spells Dragon Bolt (e) Special works Sound Effects are perfect vls/stat. hammer spec works All PVP armour available! All spirit shields work and are available Full mage bank full east drags Perfect combat difference attacking Pures Mains ::setlevel 1,2,3,4,5,6,7 99 - ect. for 99 stats No training! Skilling! Perfect eating! Vengeance Heal other! Special Restore! Veng. Other ::mb Perfect and Full ranging ::kdr! Godwars Corporal Beast! Lever In MB Full teleblock! No teleing out of wild! No spawning in Wild! Starter is 200m! ::Sell loots! ::Empty NO bank glitches[/CODE]
